---
import Layout from '@/layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	icon="beach"
	title="About Me"
	description=""
	pubDate={new Date('March 30 2026')}
	heroImage="/src/assets/hero.webp"
>
	<p>
		I'm Parth Sharma — a marketing MBA who spent years in B2B before discovering that what I actually love is making people feel smart about the world.
	</p>

	<p>
		I run Distilled by Parth, a history and geopolitics page followed by 11,000+ people. Every week I break down complex world events into something you can actually use in a conversation.
	</p>

	<p>
		Now I bring that same energy live — to corporate teams. 60 minutes, unconventional questions, one round about your own industry, and a lot of moments where someone says <em>wait, I did not know that.</em>
	</p>

	<p>
		If you want your team to leave smarter, more curious, and genuinely entertained — let's talk.
	</p>
</Layout>
